 flex-col items-end py-4 pl-8 w-full" data-sentry-component="UserMessage" data-sentry-source-file="user-message.tsx"><div class="flex flex-col items-end group/userChatBox relative" data-sentry-component="DefaultMessage" data-sentry-source-file="user-message.tsx"><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 px-4 pt-3 pb-2 !pt-0"></div><div class="px-4 py-3 bg-userChat rounded-[16px_16px_4px_16px] min-w max-w-full bg-surface-default"><p class="text-[14px] leading-[150%] break-words whitespace-break-spaces wrap-anywhere" data-sentry-element="Text" data-sentry-source-file="user-message.tsx">Build a modern CSV analysis web application called "InsightFlow" with the following specifications:

THEME &amp; DESIGN:
- Dark modern theme with glassmorphism effects
- Primary colors: Deep blue (#1e40af) with bright accent (#06b6d4)
- Clean, professional analytics dashboard aesthetic
- Use glassmorphism cards with subtle shadows and blur effects

CORE FUNCTIONALITY:
1. CSV file upload with drag &amp; drop
2. Direct OpenAI API integration for analysis
3. Interactive dashboard with charts and insights
4. Responsive design for all devices

REQUIRED PAGES:
1. Landing page with hero section
2. Upload interface
3. Loading/analysis screen
4. Results dashboard

COMPONENT REQUIREMENTS (use modern 21st.dev style components):

FROM HEROES SECTION:
- Modern hero with gradient background and animated elements
- Include title "Transform Your Data Into Actionable Insights"
- CTA button leading to upload section

FROM FILE UPLOADS:
- Drag &amp; drop file upload component with preview
- Support for CSV files only (max 5MB)
- Visual feedback during upload

FROM CARDS:
- Glassmorphism metric cards for data quality scores
- Insight cards with icons and confidence levels
- Recommendation cards with priority badges

FROM BUTTONS:
- Modern animated buttons with hover effects
- Primary CTA buttons
- Secondary navigation buttons

FROM SPINNER LOADERS:
- Smooth loading animation during AI analysis
- Progress indicators

FROM NUMBERS:
- Animated counter components for metrics
- Percentage displays with smooth transitions

FROM ALERTS:
- Success/error notifications
- File validation messages

FROM BADGES:
- Priority levels (High/Medium/Low)
- Confidence scores
- Impact indicators

TECHNICAL STACK:
- React + Vite
- TailwindCSS for styling
- Recharts for data visualization
- OpenAI API for analysis
- Lucide React for icons
- Framer Motion for animations

API REQUIREMENTS:
- Single /api/analyze endpoint
- Accept CSV data, return structured insights
- OpenAI integration with business analysis prompts
- Error handling for rate limits and failures

DASHBOARD FEATURES:
- Data quality overview (completeness, accuracy, anomalies)
- Key insights section with AI-generated findings
- Actionable recommendations with ROI estimates
- Interactive charts showing data patterns
- Export results functionality

RESPONSIVE DESIGN:
- Mobile-first approach
- Tablet and desktop optimized layouts
- Touch-friendly interactions

Please create a complete, production-ready application with all files, proper error handling, environment variables setup, and deployment configuration for Vercel. Include sample CSV data for testing.
